507
00:27:59,180 --> 00:28:00,980
She is the kindest to me.

508
00:28:06,020 --> 00:28:06,740
Well.

509
00:28:08,580 --> 00:28:10,580
Maybe it is

510
00:28:10,580 --> 00:28:11,620
